<template>
    <form class="pokemon-form">
      <input
        class="pokemon-input"
        type="text"
        name="pokemon"
        v-model="pokemonID"
        placeholder="Busca tu pokemon"
        autocomplete="off"/>
      <button
        @click="getCoin"
        type="submit"
        class="pokemon-btn"
        value=""
      >
      buscar pokemon
      </button>
    </form>
  </template>
  
  <script>
  export default {
    name: 'PxBuscador',
  
    data () {
      return {
        // es el id que se le pasa al APP
        pokemonID: 0
      }
    },
  
   

  }
  </script>
